    <h2 class="sect-title">About Thorncliffe</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1954, Thorncliffe is a mature and family-friendly community that regularly attracts hoards of homebuyers and investors alike.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Given the fact that it was built nearly half a century ago, the properties in Thorncliffe real estate primarily comprise large single-family detached houses and duplexes that have an archaic character to them. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Thorncliffe are regularly listed at an average price of $360,000. </p>
